org.graphstream.stream
Interface AttributeSink

All Known Subinterfaces:
FileSink, Graph, Layout, Pipe, ProxyPipe, Sink
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractGraph, AdjacencyListGraph, AttributePipe, DefaultGraph, FileSinkBase, FileSinkDGS, FileSinkDOT, FileSinkDynamicGML, FileSinkGML, FileSinkImages, FileSinkSVG, FileSinkSWF, FileSinkTikZ, GraphicGraph, MultiGraph, PipeAdapter, PipeBase, RMISink, SingleGraph, SinkAdapter, SpringBox, SpriteManager, ThreadProxyPipe, VerboseSink, ViewerPipe
public interface AttributeSink

Interface to listen at changes on attributes of a graph.

The graph attributes listener is called each time an attribute is added, or removed, and each time its value is changed.
